---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact | Tactisens Escape Game Toulouse" description="Contactez Tactisens Escape Game a Toulouse. Reservations groupes, renseignements, evenements. 33 Port Saint-Sauveur, 31000 Toulouse.">

  <!-- ==================== HERO COMPACT ==================== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[250px] flex items-end">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/escape-game-toulouse-tactisens-04.webp"
        alt="Escape Game Toulouse Tactisens Contact"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content relative z-10 py-10 w-full">
      <h1 class="font-share text-larger lg:text-colossal font-bold leading-none">Contact</h1>
      <nav class="text-sm mt-3 text-white/70" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white no-underline">Accueil</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-white">Contact</span>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== L'ADRESSE POUR S'EVADER ==================== -->
  <section class="bg-tac-dark-blue py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-content">
      <!-- Spirale + Titre -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <img
          src="/images/escape-game-toulouse-tactisens-31-bis.webp"
          alt=""
          class="w-[60px] h-[60px] object-contain mb-6"
        />
        <h2 class="font-share text-larger lg:text-colossal font-bold text-center leading-none tracking-[-2px]">
          <span class="text-tac-white">L'adresse</span><br />
          <span class="text-tac-orange">pour s'evader</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Two columns -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">

        <!-- LEFT: Infos pratiques -->
        <div class="space-y-8">

          <!-- Uniquement sur reservation -->
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-share text-tac-orange uppercase font-bold tracking-[2px] text-body mb-3">Uniquement sur reservation</h5>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-body leading-relaxed">
              33 Port Saint-Sauveur<br />
              31000 Toulouse<br />
              <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">(A cote du Grand Rond et de la Place Dupuy)</span>
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Horaires d'ouverture -->
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-share text-tac-orange uppercase font-bold tracking-[2px] text-body mb-3">Horaires d'ouverture</h5>
            <div class="text-white/80 text-body space-y-1">
              <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs">
                <span>Lundi a jeudi</span>
                <span>10:00 - 23:30</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs">
                <span>Vendredi</span>
                <span>10:00 - 00:30</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs">
                <span>Samedi</span>
                <span>09:00 - 00:30</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs">
                <span>Dimanche</span>
                <span>09:00 - 23:30</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Itineraire -->
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-share text-tac-orange uppercase font-bold tracking-[2px] text-body mb-3">Itineraire</h5>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-body leading-relaxed">
              Tactisens est situe au 33 Port Saint-Sauveur, en plein coeur de Toulouse, a proximite du Grand Rond et de la Place Dupuy. Facilement accessible en voiture, metro et bus.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Autres acces -->
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-share text-tac-orange uppercase font-bold tracking-[2px] text-body mb-3">Autres acces</h5>
            <ul class="text-white/80 text-body leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-none p-0">
              <li><strong class="text-white">Parking :</strong> places disponibles devant le local (dont 2 PMR), Parking Paul Sabatier (2 min), Parking Carnot (5 min)</li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Metro :</strong> Francois Verdier (ligne B, 5 min a pied)</li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Bus :</strong> lignes 14, 22, 27, 38, L1</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: Google Maps -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2889.5!2d1.4534!3d43.5947!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12aebb5c8cf2e4f3%3A0x4f45c0da8e33db72!2sTactisens!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1"
            width="100%"
            height="450"
            style="border:0; min-height:100%;"
            allowfullscreen=""
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== NOUS CONTACTER ==================== -->
  <section class="bg-tac-dark-blue py-16 lg:py-24 border-t border-white/10">
    <div class="section-content">
      <!-- Spirale + Titre -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <img
          src="/images/escape-game-toulouse-tactisens-31-bis.webp"
          alt=""
          class="w-[60px] h-[60px] object-contain mb-6"
        />
        <h2 class="font-share text-larger lg:text-colossal font-bold text-center leading-none tracking-[-2px] text-tac-white">
          Nous contacter
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Two columns -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">

        <!-- LEFT: Textes d'orientation -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6 text-white/80 text-body leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Pour toutes les informations pratiques, vous trouverez votre reponse sur notre page <a href="/faq" class="text-tac-orange hover:underline">FAQ</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Plus d'informations sur nos deux concepts de jeu ? Rendez-vous sur les pages <a href="/escape-game" class="text-tac-orange hover:underline">Escape Game</a> et <a href="/aventure-sensorielle" class="text-tac-orange hover:underline">Aventure Sensorielle</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Vous n'avez pas trouve ? Merci de nous contacter via le formulaire de contact.
          </p>
          <p>
            Pour toute demande d'offre d'emploi, merci de consulter notre page dediee.
          </p>
          <p>
            En dernier recours, vous pouvez nous appeler au <a href="tel:0534594581" class="text-tac-orange font-bold hover:underline whitespace-nowrap">05 34 59 45 81</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: Formulaire de contact -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <form class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 space-y-5" id="contact-form">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
              <div>
                <label for="nom" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Nom *</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="nom"
                  name="nom"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-tac-orange transition-colors"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="prenom" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Prenom *</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="prenom"
                  name="prenom"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-tac-orange transition-colors"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
              <div>
                <label for="societe" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Societe</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="societe"
                  name="societe"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-tac-orange transition-colors"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="telephone" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Telephone *</label>
                <input
                  type="tel"
                  id="telephone"
                  name="telephone"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-tac-orange transition-colors"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Email *</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-tac-orange transition-colors"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Votre message *</label>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                name="message"
                rows="6"
                required
                placeholder="Ecrivez votre message ici..."
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-tac-orange transition-colors resize-vertical"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
              En soumettant ce formulaire, vous acceptez que les informations saisies soient utilisees pour vous recontacter dans le cadre de votre demande. Pour en savoir plus sur la gestion de vos donnees personnelles et vos droits, consultez notre politique de confidentialite.
            </p>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-orange">Envoyer</button>
          </form>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
